articles.title: Burt, the famous croc from "Crocodile Dundee" movie, dies in Australia - CBS News
articles.description: Burt, the iconic Saltwater crocodile that appeared alongside Paul Hogan and Linda Kozlowski in the hit movie, was believed to be more than 90 years old.
articles.content:
The crocodile who became famous after his appearance in the 1986 film "Crocodile Dundee" has died, the Australian reptile and aquarium attraction where he lived announced on social media.
